SLS 26RS-4336 ORIGINAL
2026 Regular Session
SENATE RESOLUTION NO. 210
BY SENATOR BARROW
LEGISLATIVE SESSIONS. Requests appointment of a committee to notify the governor
that the legislature is ready to adjourn sine die.
1 A RESOLUTION
2 To request the appointment of a committee to notify the governor that the legislature is
3 ready to adjourn sine die.
4 THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED by the Senate of the Legislature of Louisiana that
5 a committee of five senators be appointed by the president of the Senate to serve with a like
6 committee from the House of Representatives to notify the governor that the Legislature of
7 Louisiana has completed its labors and is now ready to adjourn sine die.
